{"tid":1751730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何妖失去太多野","createTime":"2019-11-24T17:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T18:05:06.000Z","uid":332367,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"496c5f755eea65f4435c364d5004bac28ab22a81","tid":1751730,"uid":332367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:59:46.000Z","msg":"轉發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到底何妖今年失去咗幾多野？<br />\n冇咗<br />\n老豆老母山墳<br />\n博士學位<br />\n玻璃爛咗<br />\n律師冇得做<br />\n2cm皮膚<br />\n粒lin<br />\n依家連議席都冇埋<br />\n仲要已經咁老<br />\n何已完人生已完<br />\n正式可以去執葉啦<br />\n<br />\n開心到想食屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e94d687af22363455e9d9c4d36a0ca8ba54f95","tid":1751730,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:59:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏輸都好，我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a001b693d312889f66ce1d02fda01966832089ab","tid":1751730,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T18:00:13.000Z","msg":"立法會議員呀"},{"pid":"3349cabec0622509cd3da72c07d7f6afc55